video.title: Call the Midwife
video.synopsis: This period drama set in impoverished East London in the 1950s follows a newly qualified midwife and her colleagues at a nursing convent.

episodes.synopsis: Newly qualified midwife Jenny Lee arrives in the East End to embark on a challenging career alongside an order of nursing nuns.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: As Jenny Lee settles into her role, there is a new arrival at Nonnatus House, Chummy.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Jenny is placed on the nursing roster to extend her experience of community practice.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: When a baby is snatched from her pram, the local community unites to search for the child.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Jenny provides care for cancer patient Frank, and learns that love can come in many forms.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Jenny learns midwifery is full of surprises when Sister Monica Joan is put on trial.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: When an abandoned baby is discovered on the steps of the convent, the whole community comes together to provide food and try to find his mother.
episodes.title: Christmas Special 2012

episodes.synopsis: It's 1958 and the day after celebrating her birthday, Nurse Jenny Lee is assigned a patient who is trapped in an abusive marriage.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: While Chummy prepares for mission work in Sierra Leone, Cynthia loses faith in her abilities, and Jimmy walks back into Jenny's life.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Jenny is sent to a short-staffed London hospital. Back at Nonnatus House, the nuns and midwives meet a pair of twins, one of whom is pregnant.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Returning from her stint at The London Hospital, Jenny and Sister Evangelina assist at the birth of the Roberts' baby, who is born with spina bifida.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: The community pulls together to prepare for the annual Summer Fete and with the addition of a Baby Show, the midwives will be more involved than ever.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: With the advent of the mass-Xray program, Dr Turner is determined that the community will no longer live under the threat of Tuberculosis.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Cynthia finds herself administering daily insulin injections to diabetic John Lacey, a man who consistently belittles his wife Annie.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Chummy and PC Noakes settle back down to life in Poplar and Jenny's own jubilation comes in the form of potential love interest Alec.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: The residents of Poplar prepare for Christmas, but an unexploded bomb is discovered, throwing festivities into chaos.
episodes.title: Christmas Special 2013

episodes.synopsis: Sister Monica Joan holds the key to the diagnosis of a mystery illness.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Trixie's feathers are ruffled when Jenny is promoted to "Acting Sister" by Sister Julienne.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Shelagh suffers devastating news and the midwives help pregnant inmates at Holloway Prison.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Jenny rushes to Alec's side when he is taken to the hospital after a horrific accident.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: When a woman with Down's syndrome discovers she is pregnant, she faces a hard decision.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Patsy struggles to adapt to the unpredictable and chaotic working life of midwifery.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Sister Julienne must talk new mother Pamela down when she is found on the edge of a pier.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Shelagh and Dr. Turner nervously await life-changing news from the Adoption Society.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: A present-day Jennifer recalls her youth at Nonnatus House; Chummy and Patsy bring joy to the festivities; Cynthia makes a life-changing decision.

episodes.synopsis: An encounter with a needy child forces Trixie to see a darker side of life; Nonnatus House welcomes a new nurse; Tom plans a romantic surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: A problematic birth causes Barbara to doubt herself; a man from Sister Julienne's past returns; the new nurse fails to impress Sister Evangelina.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Poplar suffers a mysterious outbreak of dysentery; an expectant couple's life is turned upside down when the husband is arrested for moral indecency.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: The midwives are in for a busy night when Sister Winifred focuses her efforts on Poplar's prostitutes. Cracks appear in Trixie and Tom's relationship.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Sister Julienne's faith is tested when a mother refuses medicine for her newborn. Dr. Turner's role in the case forces him to face his own demons.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: A diabetic teen faces heartbreak when she falls pregnant through a secret romance; the midwives get involved with a settlement of Irish Travellers.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Motherhood intertwines the lives of estranged friends in an unexpected way; Barbara and Sister Mary Cynthia aid an elderly man and his steadfast wife.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Trixie and Sister Mary Cynthia team up to support a deaf mother-to-be; Fred's daughter is less than delighted about his upcoming wedding.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: As Tom and Shelagh scramble to prepare for a televised concert, a mother grapples with painful memories, and a sudden disappearance rocks Nonnatus.
episodes.title: Christmas Special 2015: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The nuns' search grows desperate. Meanwhile, a measles outbreak threatens to derail the Christmas show, and Iris gets the surprise of her life.
episodes.title: Christmas Special 2015: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The birth of a baby with severe deformities leaves a family and the midwives reeling. Trixie's new passion stirs up tensions with Sister Julienne.

episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: The outbreak of a rare disease takes an emotional toll on Patsy, while a young teacher suffers painful repercussions for her unplanned pregnancy.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Sister Julienne makes a disturbing discovery in the hospital maternity ward, and an ambitious student suddenly finds his future in limbo.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: A young mother's troubled past comes back to haunt her as she struggles to connect with her baby. Dr. Turner gets a wake-up call from his own son.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Shame allows an attacker to continue preying on women. Efforts to hide a teen's pregnancy take an alarming turn. Dr. Turner's family plans a surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: A proud transient woman resists medical and family assistance. A crisis helps distant newlyweds to bond. Sister Evangelina returns, but is changed.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Turner has a horrifying realization. Nonnatus House is dealt an unexpected blow. Swift action is taken to ensure a baby isn't born out of wedlock.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.title: Christmas Special 2016: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Myra's condition worsens. A lack of water spurs Tom to visit a bitter landowner. Trixie makes a shocking discovery about Roza's long-awaited baby.
episodes.title: Christmas Special 2016: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: A sudden change in management rocks Nonnatus House. A young mother takes a brave stand against her abusive husband. Shelagh reveals a joyful surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: While trying to find an appropriate home for a 21-year-old orphan with Down syndrome, Fred and Sister Monica Joan stumble upon an upsetting discovery.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Barbara and Tom must fast-track their plans. The day Shelagh has been waiting for finally arrives. Trixie sees the dark side of contraceptive pills.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: As a historically harsh winter hits Poplar on Boxing Day 1962, Valerie is left shaken by a complicated delivery, while Barbara and Tom get big news.

episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Two new nuns arrive at Nonnatus House. A feverish Sister Monica Joan disappears. The midwives must secretly help a model who had an illegal procedure.
